    <section class="hp-lead-sidebar">
      <div class="hp-lead">
        <h2><a href="/architecture/overview/">System Architecture</a></h2>
        <p>
          The Base node is composed of 8 crate groups spanning consensus, execution,
          block building, fault proofs, and shared infrastructure. Data flows from
          Ethereum L1 through a derivation pipeline into the execution layer, with
          Flashblocks providing 200ms preconfirmations.
        </p>
        <pre class="hp-ascii-diagram">                     L1 (Ethereum)
                          |
          ┌───────────────┼───────────────┐
          v               v               v
     ┌─────────┐   ┌───────────┐   ┌───────────┐
     │consensus│   │   proof   │   │  builder   │
     │ (kona)  │   │  (kona)   │   │(flashblocks│
     └────┬────┘   └───────────┘   │  + core)  │
          │                         └─────┬─────┘
          v                               v
     ┌─────────┐                   ┌───────────┐
     │ client  │◄─────────────────►│ execution │
     │(node +  │                   │  (EVM +   │
     │ engine) │                   │  payload) │
     └────┬────┘                   └───────────┘
          │
          v
     ┌─────────┐   ┌───────────┐   ┌───────────┐
     │ shared  │   │   alloy   │   │   infra   │
     │(prims,  │   │ (types +  │   │(binaries +│
     │ utils)  │   │  codecs)  │   │  tooling) │
     └─────────┘   └───────────┘   └───────────┘</pre>
        <a href="/architecture/overview/" class="hp-text-link">Full architecture overview</a>
      </div>

